{"tid":1538464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第二波。護聲教學 - 都係嗌到把聲拆晒嘅人同我入嚟！！！同我睇到最後！","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:38:32.000Z","uid":300163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84fb19c15a550a44b0e47b5d2ea66a1cb8d2bfaa","tid":1538464,"uid":300163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又係我</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫左你哋鍚住把聲，出親街個個嗌到把聲傷晒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔緊要！今日再教多啲，護聲！<br />\n唔該大家睇到最後，有練習，好短<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><br />\n嗌完做，得閒做，日日做</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">答應我，睇到最後！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1。飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲暖水</span></span></strong><br />\n如果你覺得自己飲夠，再飲多啲<br />\n水入左去身體，都要花<span style=\"color: orange;\">1～2個鐘</span>先會帶水份到聲帶<br />\n所以，9嗌前一兩個鐘，好定飲暖水<br />\n嗌完一定要啦當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">注意返：咖啡、食煙人士，要再飲多少少，因為本身呢兩舊嘢會整乾你喉嚨；容易熱氣人士，同樣都係 </span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2。瞓得夠</span></span></strong><br />\n我知大家好難做到<br />\n但<span style=\"color: orange;\">一定要瞓</span>！！！！！！！！！<br />\n另外，聲帶要休息，就係唔講嘢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3。蒸氣</span></span></strong><br />\n依家！<br />\n即刻同我<span style=\"color: red;\">煲熱啲水</span>！<br />\n擺塊面埋去！<br />\n最少5分鐘！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">因為蒸氣可以入聲帶，直接滋潤聲帶同周圍肌肉</span></span><br />\n當然，只係表面，就好似你搓嘢向塊面咁<br />\n暫時性質，最緊要都係飲水<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4。練習</span></span></strong><br />\n我上網搵左啲簡單易明嘅練習俾大家，大家得閒記得就做下<br />\n睇落好ON 9 ，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">絕。對。有。用！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">綀習一</span></span></strong> (4:18-4:33) <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMy7nlV68_ho%3Ft%3D258&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEqwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=16c1df18\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=258</a><br />\n音域上盡量搵返自己舒服！<br />\n<strong><ins>最緊要舒服！</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">綀習二</span></span></strong> (4:56-5:05) <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMy7nlV68_ho%3Ft%3D296&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEqwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=a5edebe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=296</a><br />\n<em>（唔駛懷疑，同一條link ）</em><br />\n呢個一樣，都係自己舒服位置<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔駛高音！！！！</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">反而我鼓勵低音啲<br />\n但！！！<br />\n個種係舒服的低音！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">綀習三</span></span></strong> (5:15 - 5:25) <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMy7nlV68_ho%3Ft%3D316&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEqwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=957dc27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/My7nlV68_ho?t=316</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個好強烈推介！！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講<br />\n如果<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">開聲</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">練習一/練習二</span></span></strong> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自己音域</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">嗌完，放鬆把聲</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">練習二/練習三</span></span></strong> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">相對較低音域！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><br />\n嗌完做，得閒做，日日做</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><br />\n嗌完做，得閒做，日日做</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><br />\n嗌完做，得閒做，日日做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f5d6cdd416938a12637692de94b7f4d04b16f858","tid":1538464,"uid":300163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fb19c15a550a44b0e47b5d2ea66a1cb8d2bfaa","